title: Need for Speed Collector's Series
description:
Need For Speed Collector's Series
Well, not really. I've just downloaded the games and put them together. Includes:

NFS: Underground (version 1.4)
NFS: Underground 2 (version 1.2)
NFS: Most Wanted BE (version 1.3)


Install: extract anywhere you want and play. All games are already updated and with no-CD patch applied.

Uninstall: delete extracted folder.

Tested on my ancient Athlon 64 X2, 4Gb RAM, GeForce GT520, Windows 7 64bit. Perfectly working.
